   * @param n_long N nodes (0 to N-1)
   * @param edges Array of edges [[u, v, w], ...]
   * @param source_long Source node
   * @param target_long Target node
   * @param k_long Max heavy edges allowed
   * @return Minimum threshold or -1
   */
